          {
            title: 'Stop building the platform — use one that is already built',
            body: 'EKS gives you raw Kubernetes. Getting from EKS to a production-grade platform takes 6–18 months of engineering effort. Stakater Cloud ships ArgoCD, Tekton, OpenBao, Prometheus, Grafana, Loki, Jaeger, multi-tenancy and more — pre-built and production-ready on day one.',
            icon: 'M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z',
          },
          {
            title: 'OpenShift, not just Kubernetes',
            body: 'OpenShift ships with stronger security defaults than vanilla Kubernetes: built-in security hardening, developer console, integrated image registry, enterprise support from Red Hat. EKS gives you plain upstream Kubernetes — every enterprise feature is an add-on your team must wire and maintain.',
            icon: 'M9 3H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v4m6-6h10a2 2 0 012 2v4M9 3v18m0 0h10a2 2 0 002-2V9M9 21H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V9m0 0h18',
