          {
            title: 'Complete developer platform, no assembly required',
            body: 'AKS provisions and patches the cluster — the platform above it is your responsibility. Stakater Cloud includes ArgoCD, Tekton, OpenBao, Prometheus, Grafana, Loki, Jaeger, MTO, Velero and more — all pre-configured, all managed by us. No platform team required.',
            icon: 'M4 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM14 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM4 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2zM14 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2z',
