            title: 'No Google Cloud dependency for EU-regulated workloads',
            body: 'GKE runs on Google Cloud — a US company subject to the US CLOUD Act. For GDPR, DORA and NIS2, Stakater Cloud offers a cleaner position: Netherlands data center, operated by Stakater AB (Sweden), with no US hyperscaler in your supply chain. ISO 27001:2022 and ISO 9001:2015 certified.',
